stw_read_meta_yaml.Rd

Create metadata-object from YAML

stw_read_meta_yaml(file)

Arguments

file

location of yaml file

Value

Object with S3 class stw_meta

Examples

stw_read_meta_yaml(system.file("metadata/diamonds.yml", package = "steward"))
